<br>
1. The purpose of this thread is to post character backgrounds.<br>
2. Each person may only post once to this thread.<br>
3. Posts that off topic will be deleted.<br>
4. Folks are STRONGLY encouraged to edit their backgrounds and keep them up to date.<br>
<br>
That's it. You can use any format you like, or follow one of the examples below. <p>Nysa, Priestess of Erolissi<br>
